headline: MSCI to Host Virtual Open House: Custom Indexes in Focus
summary: NEW YORK, September 17, 2025--MSCI Inc. ("MSCI" or the "Company") (NYSE: MSCI) will host a virtual open house spotlighting its custom index capabilities on Thursday, September 25. Participants will include Jana Haines, Head of Index, and Jeremy Ulan, Head of Investor Relations and Treasurer.
